name: RYN_WHT_MED_INSURANCE
description: Ryan White table for patient's medical insurance status.

columns.name: REGISTRY_DATA_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier (.1 item) for the registry data record.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number for the information associated with this record. Multiple pieces of information can be associated with this record.

columns.name: RYN_WHT_MED_INSURANCE_C_NAME
entries: Medicaid, CHIP, or other public plan
Veterans Health Administration (VA), military health care (TRICARE) and other military plans

columns.name: RYN_WHT_INSURANCE_OTHER
columns.description: If the patient's Ryan White reporting insurance is Other, this item specifies what the other insurance is.

columns.name: RYN_WHT_INSURANCE_DATE
columns.description: The start date corresponding to the patient's Ryan White insurance.

columns.name: RYN_WHT_INSURANCE_FULL_LIS_YN
columns.description: Indicates whether the patient's insurance is a Low-Income Subsidy for Ryan White reporting.

columns.name: RW_INSURANCE_HIGH_RISK_POOL_YN
columns.description: Indicates whether the patient's insurance is a High-Risk Pool for Ryan White reporting.
